A new alloy
In the mountains of Jygran, there is a metal ore from which a new alloy with great properties can be made.
#subobj 1
Take the ore
Suitable ore can be found in the mountains to the west of the city walls.
#subobj 2
Find the forge
The forge can be found to the west of the place behind the river. Traveling there should not be dangerous.
#subobj 3
Smelting alloy
The forge is free and still operational, you can use it to smelt new alloy.